AFFIDAVIT OF NON-RECEIPT OF MAINTENANCE ASSESSMENTS
OF THE TRINITY OAKS HOMEOWNERS' ASSOCIATION OF BEXAR COUNTY, INC.
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR
"Notice is hereby given that there exists a lien for unpaid maintenance assessments assessed by TRINITY OAKS
HOMEOWNERS' ASSOCIATION OF BEXAR COUNTY, INC ., for non-payment by the owner of the subject property and such
maintenance assessments being in accordance with the Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for Trinity Oaks
Subdivision as recorded in Volume 10881, Page 1612, et seq. in the Official Public Records of Bexar County, Texas; and
Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for Trinity Oaks Unit 3, Planned Unit Development and Provisions for
the Trinity Oaks Subdivision, as recorded in Volume 11221, Page 401, et seq. in the Official Public Records of Bexar County,
Texas. The property subject to this Affidavit is as follows, to-wit:
SUBJECT PROPERTY:
Address:
2802 Cascade Mist, San Antonio, Texas 78261
Legal Description:
Lot 25, Block 6, Trinity Oaks, Unit 3, Planned Unit Development, a subdivision in
Bexar County, Texas, according to map or plat thereof recorded in Volume 9563,
Page 183, Deed and Plat Records of Bexar County, Texas.
Last Known Owners:
Rene Ibarra, Jr.
Last Known Address:
2802 Cascade Mist, San Antonio, Texas 78261
Amount of Delinquent:
$1,463.69
Assessments and Fees:
Amounts are subject to continued accrual of late fees, interest and collection costs
which shall be automatically added to the lien amount.
Executed this 29 day of Dicemb 2021.
TRINITY OAKS HOMEOWNERS' ASSOCIATION OF BEXAR COUNTY, INC.
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR
By:
ALAMO MANAGEMENT GROUP
By:
JOANN LAREDO,
Legal Specialist
c/o Alamo Management Group
2611 N. Loop 1604 W. Suite 100
San Antonio, Texas 78258
This instrument is acknowledged and sworn to before me on this 20 day of recenlo. , 2021, by JOANN
LAREDO, LEGAL SPECIALIST of ALAMO MANAGEMENT GROUP, on behalf of TRINITY OAKS HOMEOWNERS'
ASSOCIATION OF BEXAR COUNTY, INC.
AFTER RECORDING, RETURN TO:
MICHAEL B. THURMAN
THURMAN & PHILLIPS, P.C.
4093 De Zavala Road
Notary Public in and for the State of Texas
ASHLYN BOOTH
Notary Public, State of Texas
My Comm. Exp. 12-10-2022
ID No. 13182693-3
